title: RHOBH: New Year's Irresolution
description:
The most buzzworthy season of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills in ages came to a conclusion this week as the women join Crystal to celebrate Chinese New Year's. It's not the most exciting episode, despite Kyle's best efforts to destroy Sutton and Erika's relationship. What did you think of the finale?

**Watch the recap with Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/57136840
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
